  "texts": [
    "\"How intensely did you feel your heartbeat?\"",
    "Each scale had anchors of \"not at all\" and \"extremely\" on the two ends.",
    "Numerical scores could range from 0 to 100.",
    "To model behavior on the heartbeat tapping task, we first divided each task time series into intervals corresponding to the periods of time directly before and after each heartbeat.",
    "Potentially perceivable heartbeats were based on the timing of the peak of the electrocardiogram (EKG) R-wave (signaling electrical depolarization of the atrioventricular neurons of the heart) + 200 milliseconds (ms)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}